<title>KALVARY AH KA HRUAI CH126</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ka nunnak Bawi kan thangthat lai, Sunpar nang ca si seh, Na hling
 luchin ka philh sual lai. Kalvary ah ka hruai.

[C1]
   Gethsemani na thlacamnak, Na tahhramnak vialte he khan, Na dawtnak
   ka philh nakhnga lo, Kalvary ah ka hruai.

[V2]
 An in vuinak thlan ka hmuhsak, Lunghno in an in tah, Ceunak puan
 thuamh in vanmi nih, Nangmah kha an in ven.

[C2]
   Gethsemani na thlacamnak, Na tahhramnak vialte he khan, Na dawtnak
   ka philh nakhnga lo, Kalvary ah ka hruai.

[V3]
 Meri bang zingah laksawng he, Na sin ka ratter tuah, Na thlan lawngmi
 kha ka hmuhsak, Kalvary ah ka hruai.

[C3]
   Gethsemani na thlacamnak, Na tahhramnak vialte he khan, Na dawtnak
   ka philh nakhnga lo, Kalvary ah ka hruai.

[V4]
 Bawipa, nang ca nifa vailam, Put awk ka lung a si, Na ngaihchiatnak in
 ve ka duh, Kei ca na in dih cang.

[C4]
   Gethsemani na thlacamnak, Na tahhramnak vialte he khan, Na dawtnak
   ka philh nakhnga lo, Kalvary ah ka hruai.</lyrics>
<key>Eb</key>
</song>